---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
import FooterComponent from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const usageSnippet = `---
import { Footer } from 'comet-astro';

---
<Footer
  brand="Comet"
  brandUrl="/"
  socialLinks=[
    { href: 'https://twitter.com', label: 'Twitter', external: true },
    { href: 'https://github.com', label: 'GitHub', external: true }
  ]
  legalLinks=[
    { href: '/legal/privacy', label: 'Privacy' },
    { href: '/legal/imprint', label: 'Imprint' }
  ]
  variant="detailed"
/>`;
---

<DocsLayout
  seoTitle="Footer"
  seoDescription="Accessible, WCAG AAA footer with brand, social, legal, and external links."
>
  <section class="space-y-4">
    <p class="text-base text-slate-100">
      The Footer component provides a responsive foundation for site-wide footers,
      including brand attribution, social links, legal notices, and additional external
      resources. All interactive elements meet WCAG AAA contrast targets and ship with
      focus outlines by default.
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-slate-200">
      Use the <code>variant</code> prop to swap between compact layouts and more detailed,
      multi-row link groups. Each link automatically exposes screen-reader labels when it
      opens a new tab.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-8 space-y-6">
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800/70 bg-slate-900/40 p-6 shadow-lg">
      <FooterComponent
        brand="Comet"
        brandUrl="/"
        socialLinks={[
          { href: 'https://twitter.com', label: 'Twitter', external: true },
          { href: 'https://github.com', label: 'GitHub', external: true },
        ]}
        legalLinks={[
          { href: '/legal/privacy', label: 'Privacy' },
          { href: '/legal/imprint', label: 'Imprint' },
        ]}
        externalLinks={[
          { href: 'https://status.comet.app', label: 'Status', external: true },
        ]}
        variant="detailed"
      />
    </div>
    <pre class="overflow-auto rounded-xl border border-slate-800/70 bg-slate-950/60 p-4 text-sm text-slate-200">
      <code>{usageSnippet}</code>
    </pre>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-8 space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Props</h2>
    <dl class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-800/60 bg-slate-900/40 p-4">
        <dt class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-300">brand?</dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">Brand or site name text. Defaults to “Your Project”.</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-800/60 bg-slate-900/40 p-4">
        <dt class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-300">brandUrl?</dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">Optional homepage link for the brand label.</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-800/60 bg-slate-900/40 p-4">
        <dt class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-300">socialLinks?</dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">Array of social link objects ({`{ href, label, external? }`} ).</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-800/60 bg-slate-900/40 p-4">
        <dt class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-300">legalLinks?</dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">Links for privacy policy, imprint, and other legal pages.</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-800/60 bg-slate-900/40 p-4">
        <dt class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-300">externalLinks?</dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">Additional links (status pages, partner resources, etc.).</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-800/60 bg-slate-900/40 p-4">
        <dt class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-300">variant?</dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Visual layout variant: <code>"simple"</code> (single-row flex) or <code>"detailed"</code>
          (stacked sections). Defaults to <code>"simple"</code>.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-800/60 bg-slate-900/40 p-4">
        <dt class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-300">showBrand?</dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">Toggle brand/copyright visibility. Defaults to true.</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-800/60 bg-slate-900/40 p-4">
        <dt class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-300">showYear?</dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">Display the current year alongside the brand.</dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </section>
</DocsLayout>
